  "title": "Nutraceuticals must remain OTC products to drive preventive healthcare: IDMA",
  "summary": "Calling nutraceuticals fundamentally different from pharmaceutical drugs, IDMA said preserving their OTC status is critical to improving consumer access, supporting preventive healthcare and advancing India's Viksit Bharat 2047 vision.",
